{"tid":1102502,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有晒預感Joker都應該會仆直","createTime":"2019-04-11T18:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T00:16:05.000Z","uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"19d576df7322dad58dfbddf8e069e2cd69ef46e2","tid":1102502,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"因為喺連登要踩低DC任何戲真係好撚容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果套野算合格<br />\n咁個公式都不外乎係話<br />\n導演今次拍得算好努力<br />\n但實際睇落依然令人感到辛苦唔適應<br />\n劇本 剪接 色調 想抄marvel結果失去原有風格同節奏<br />\n<br />\n食老本思維內容唔討好<br />\n睇完難免覺得好失望<br />\nDC次次都眼高手低做得唔夠好<br />\n難聽講又係拍咗套垃圾出黎<br />\n好聽啲就可以話仲有進步空間 浪費晒祖昆馮力士既演釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者套戲到時真係好垃圾 邊個知<br />\n咁就唔駛咁婉轉 可以直接屌柒DC添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da3ded32d32b43e43d28bdba8dd8370f7cb0702","tid":1102502,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62bf5828b9adfb817f6699dfac56d4ad4a30ebcc","tid":1102502,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6da3ded32d32b43e43d28bdba8dd8370f7cb0702","tid":1102502,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"我睇完就算覺得好睇應該都會照搵啲嘢去踩<br />\n因為反DC永遠有班人支持<br />\n可以攞認同感係開心事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82472b7f0e492a69823e74434b927172303e3757","tid":1102502,"uid":193476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"joaquin phoenix 唔會做垃圾戲，好期待呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce07da3e7e80c91098aa9026ba404e3c33d091e7","tid":1102502,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":9,